optimized_sql: WITH filtered_item AS (SELECT i_item_sk, i_item_id, i_item_desc, i_current_price FROM item WHERE i_current_price BETWEEN 17 AND 47 AND i_manufact_id IN (639, 169, 138, 339)), inventory_date_exists AS (SELECT i_item_sk, i_item_id, i_item_desc, i_current_price FROM filtered_item WHERE EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM inventory JOIN date_dim ON inv_date_sk = d_date_sk WHERE inv_item_sk = filtered_item.i_item_sk AND d_date BETWEEN CAST('1999-07-09' AS DATE) AND (CAST('1999-07-09' AS DATE) + INTERVAL 60 DAY) AND inv_quantity_on_hand BETWEEN 100 AND 500)), store_sales_exists AS (SELECT i_item_id, i_item_desc, i_current_price FROM inventory_date_exists WHERE EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM store_sales WHERE ss_item_sk = inventory_date_exists.i_item_sk)) SELECT i_item_id, i_item_desc, i_current_price FROM store_sales_exists GROUP BY i_item_id, i_item_desc, i_current_price ORDER BY i_item_id LIMIT 100
